---
title: Grilled Pork & Charred Asparagus Couscous with Cheesy Greens & Herby Mayo
description: Bring the Mediterranean to your next barbecue with this mouthwatering meal. Tender pork is seasoned to perfection and grilled over the flame for ultimate flavour. Charred asparagus tossed into fluffy couscous and a drizzle of herby mayo adds freshness and creaminess, rounding out a dish that’s bursting with summer vibes.
